ed kingdom prior to this appointment he was senior advisor to the chief executive officer of schlumberger based in houston texas united states gérard joined schlumberger in  after completing a masters of engineering at the ecole nationale superieure de laeronautique et de lespace supaero france he began his oilfield career as a wireline field engineer quickly progressing into operations management with assignments in spain italy france nigeria algeria and venezuela he then transitioned into personnel and during the next twenty years worked with most of the company’s oilfield services business sectors from  to  he was personnel manager of the company’s drilling group and during this time was responsible for integrating the organizations of several major oilfield services companies purchased by schlumberger including smith mi and geoservices he is one of the founders of partnerjobcom for which he has served as treasurer since  this is a nonprofit association that includes several major corporations and organizations that value global mobility and spouse support as members it aims to facilitate the geographical mobility of dualcareer partners by offering a worldwide database where employers can connect with international candidates and where talented candidates can find global job opportunities gérard joined the board of the foundation in march  to continue to lend his support to the schlumberger longterm commitment to promoting women in technology in the world at large   schlumberger limited all rights reserved  privacy  terms  help  site map  contact   slb gerard martellozo insider trades for schlumberger ltd bulletin investor alert london markets close in currencies futures metals stocks expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close schlumberger ltd nyse slb go set alerts find a broker join td ameritrade market index overview profile news charts financials historical quotes analyst estimates option